Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PRE------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像迷宫一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘…甘油炸药？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这些全受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 不会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道追兵几时会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雪好像过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利和中央来的部下共计3名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找准破绽解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战计划仅由这里在场人员执行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对北方司令部的士兵也要严格保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…迈尔斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说解决掉 难道是要杀了他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不赞成杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封住他的炼金术 让他交待情报比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为他会乖乖招供吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他活着太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他的部下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说不定也是被迫变成合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法才服从他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是「说不定」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为怀疑就杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将那件事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还有其他方法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了布里格斯的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍一大意就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那种天真的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会断送你和同伴的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不需要愚钝之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会收拾掉金布利及其他两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说都是个小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界想贯彻不杀真是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我也有过那种时期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这年纪 久经沙场就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀人比杀人还困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利克兄弟选择了困难的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些好事之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过我也有点羡慕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「拉萨亚纳」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让人长寿的灵药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是说贤者之石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…「将一切金属变成金 返老还童」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「奥雷利安」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是金的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老总是和金有联系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为写这本书的斯卡的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了新国炼丹术影响吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们新国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之人就是真正的人 被称为「真人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是「完全的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金也是完全的金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也有把「真人」叫做「金人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的人就是金人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另有一说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为把炼金术传到新国的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个金发金瞳长生不老的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像爱德和阿尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利穿过山脉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在赶往布里格斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你们都跟我来…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 我背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（喂喂 HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把雪踩实开道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（没人听见吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们跟在后面就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（喂喂 HELP ME）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喂～～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喂～HELP ME～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（有人吗～）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 糟糕糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心陷到坑里 结果就被埋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爬过山先过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬山？在那暴风雪中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不绕道直接过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急联络？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央军进入了布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯特朗少将也被召去中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在去要塞很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好藏去别处了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别处是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这里不远应该有个叫阿斯别克的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说我有些同胞藏身在那里的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔的贫民窟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老大 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔突然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利不会起疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 哥哥会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3班 3名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4班 5名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 人齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始分头搜索各自负责的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是　明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要说「好」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 但是这个行动好不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 金布利看过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 金布利他们要搜索哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城中心有个大纵坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要从那里进去调查坑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是北方兵不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只带中央的部下去查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 那家伙发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在纵坑附近占好狙击点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在坑道入口找找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有复数的足迹就没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这距离可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调查坑道的话交给布里格斯兵比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面好像很复杂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会特地前来拖住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来就是这里没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想快点找到斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么你是在狙击手占好位之前来拖时间的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围杀气这么重 当然会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没白从伊修瓦尔战中生还啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能只瞄准金布利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪 慎重点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混账 用雪遮挡视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 大叔你们也是合成兽啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对方也一样 半斤八两…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么差的视野条件下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别想逃过我们灵敏的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯少校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们习惯在视野不良的地方战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要进到雪雾里来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 可恶又要变矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘油炸药？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 不要靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西早就受潮没法用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你们知道甘油炸药的原料是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝化甘油？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硝化甘醇还有木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有硝酸铵什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么硝酸铵是怎么生成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单 硝酸和氨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子太灵有时候也不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮家伙已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦不用担心人质就反了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想让你把知道的所有事情都给我吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚大病初愈 要对付年轻人还真要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也没工夫跟你耗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我用一下这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然主动亮出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能使用炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真这么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决心不杀人的确是了不起的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在战场上这会成为软肋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一瞬你没给我致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种幼稚导致了你的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵坑塌方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狠心 连我们一起砸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利那家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 又被拖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 被拖走？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}喂 怎么了 穿盔甲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂…被拖到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔！阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂被拖走？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 之前发生过类似事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这样让她流泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己伤得更重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要有人把刺入腹部的东西拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们把那根钢筋拔出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可还是敌人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没有命令我们杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拔出来的话你会立即大出血而死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔出来的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大出血之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用炼金术封住伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有医疗方面炼金术的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我想进行人体练成的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微研究过个大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在你内脏严重受损啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你又不像金布利先生有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有贤者之石可以用我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿命可能会稍微缩短点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自己的幼稚招致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自己来收拾残局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不大清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但确实没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的生命看做一种能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和贤者之石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我现在就是一个灵魂份的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的…感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用人命的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便把人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有完全治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把没伤的组织连起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强止血的应急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得赶紧让医生看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得赶紧去追金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然大家都…有危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这状态打起来完全没胜算的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金布利先生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用敬语了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我们也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就此跟那个混蛋划清界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就当我们在这里死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是自由身了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…这家伙怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去以后赶快找医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为打破僵局 开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要奇思妙想与行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了隐藏着的真实的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握着通往胜利的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这是日积月累的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第42话 反击的先兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 战争即将爆发
